&lt;p&gt;From short-term loans to money transfers and prepaid cards, we power the products, technology, and operations that connect over a million customers a year to the money they need, when they need it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At MFSG, we come together across teams and departments to create something bigger than ourselves: solutions that remove barriers and give people access to money they might not get anywhere else. Whether you&#39;re solving problems, building systems, or shaping strategy, your work fuels real support for real people.&lt;/p&gt;
