&lt;li&gt;Support current-state analysis to identify inefficiencies, bottlenecks, and improvement opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in applying process improvement methodologies such as Lean Six Sigma&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to designing and implementing optimized workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stakeholder Engagement &amp;amp; Facilitation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate interviews and support workshops (e.g., kaizen sessions) to gather insights from stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with business teams to understand operational challenges and requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Documentation &amp;amp; Process Design&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document workflows, standard operating procedures (SOPs), and process maps&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the development and rollout of new or improved processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
