&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Associate degree or bachelor&#39;s degree in software engineering, computer science, information technology, information systems, computer engineering, or an equivalent combination of education and relevant work experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ITIL certification or other relevant industry certifications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;EXPERIENCE&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum of 3-4 years’ working experience within a helpdesk call center or IT Service Delivery arena.&lt;/li&gt;
